title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Blue Mountains
subTitle: Som's mother sees her son's selection for a singing reality show as a second chance to fulfil her own dreams. However, complications arise when he faces a quick defeat.

title: Amar Akbar Anthony
subTitle: Three brothers, each raised in different religious households, reunite after many years in a chance encounter. They set out to take revenge on those responsible for separating them.

title: Amrit
subTitle: A widowed man and woman face abuse from their respective children and seek comfort from each other instead.

title: Charitraheen
subTitle: Destiny separates two lovers, Inder and Rama, and Inder marries Kamala. However, events take an unprecedented turn when Inder and Rama cross paths again years later.

title: Kya Yehi Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Rahul falls in love with Sandhya, a fellow college student, but realises that she does not reciprocate his feelings. Undeterred by her rejection, he still pursues her but pays a huge price for it.

title: Prem Geet
subTitle: A poet falls in love with a girl and later realises that she is terminally ill. Despite being aware of her condition, he decides to marry her and keep her happy.

title: Amba
subTitle: When Amba gets her son Rajendra arrested for sexually assaulting their servant's daughter, Rajendra's wife wreaks havoc into their lives as she vows to avenge him.

title: Samadhi
subTitle: Lakhan Singh gives up his life of crime when he falls in love and marries Champa. However, things take a turn when she falls sick and he is forced to become a criminal again.

title: Har Dil Jo Pyar Karega
subTitle: Raj, an aspiring singer, rescues Pooja, the daughter of a wealthy man, from an accident. However, he soon finds himself in a web of complications when he falls in love with her best friend.

title: Bheja Fry 2
subTitle: Bhushan, a tax inspector, meets Ajit, a businessman evading an IT raid, on a cruise ship. In a bizarre turn of events, Ajit and Bhushan get lost on an isolated island.

title: Bheja Fry 2
subTitle: Bhushan, a tax inspector, meets Ajit, a businessman evading an IT raid, on a cruise ship. In a bizarre turn of events, Ajit and Bhushan get lost on an isolated island.

title: Falak
subTitle: Fueled by a deep desire for revenge, two young boys mature into strong-minded adults and set out to secure the justice denied to their father years ago.

title: Judaai
subTitle: Shashikant and Gauri get married in honour of his late father's will. But, marital problems soon arise when Gauri suspects him of having an affair, leading to a chain of misunderstandings.

title: Phamous
subTitle: Radhe looks up to Kadak Singh, a local politician, but holds a grudge against his partner, Ram Tripathi. However, things reach a boiling point when Tripathi sets his sights on Radhe's wife, Lalli.

title: Johny Mera Naam
subTitle: Two brothers who excel in boxing are separated in childhood and take different paths after their father, a police officer, is murdered by a gangster.

title: Jaali Note
subTitle: On a mission to stop a gang from circulating fake currency, Inspector Dinesh must adopt various disguises. As he chases the culprits, Dinesh unveils a dark secret.

title: Bombai Ka Babu
subTitle: Babu, who kills a man, is blackmailed by Bhagat into assuming the identity of a wealthy heir, Kundan, for his money. However, things get complicated when Babu falls in love with Kundan's sister.

title: Joshila
subTitle: A jailor's daughter falls for a prisoner poet, believing him wrongly convicted and strives to prove his innocence and secure his release.

title: Desi Tadka
subTitle: The newest compilation of preppy Punjabi music is played continuously for the viewers with a preference for Indian dance beats.

title: Asli Naqli
subTitle: Anand, a rich youngster, denounces his wealth to establish himself independently. However, he keeps struggling in the big city until Renu, a middle-class woman, helps him, and he falls for her.

title: Amir Garib
subTitle: Mohanlal, a musician and a thief, robs rich people and distributes the money amongst the poor. However, things take a turn when he falls for Sunita, a wealthy man's daughter.

title: Dil Vil Pyar Vyar
subTitle: Dev, Vishal and Hrithik enter a singing competition. However, life is complicated for them as they face numerous obstacles in their personal lives which slowly bring out the best in them.

title: Dil Vil Pyar Vyar
subTitle: Dev, Vishal and Hrithik enter a singing competition. However, life is complicated for them as they face numerous obstacles in their personal lives which slowly bring out the best in them.

title: Maachis
subTitle: Jaswant is arrested and tortured for a crime he did not commit. On seeing his friend's condition, Kripal joins an extremist group in order to bring down the government.

title: S.P. Chauhan
subTitle: Satpal Chauhan, a social worker from Haryana, works for women empowerment and also strives to create an alcohol-free society. However, while pursuing his goals, he faces several hardships.

title: Pathar Ke Insan
subTitle: Talented sisters, Sita and Lata, are renowned performing artists. However, the rivalry between them leads to a competition with far-reaching consequences.

title: Ustadi Ustad Se
subTitle: A flood separates childhood friends Seema and Rajesh. Years later, when she reconciles with him and the two plan to get together, things go awry with the arrival of a mysterious woman.

title: Namak Halaal
subTitle: Arjun, a youngster, works at a hotel owned by Raja and serves him faithfully. However, when he learns about a plot to kill Raja, he decides to save him from harm at any cost.

title: Aap Beati
subTitle: Geeta and her father undergo several hardships to ensure that Prakash gets an education abroad. However, things take a turn when, upon his return, he marries a rich girl.

title: Pyar Ki Jeet
subTitle: Anand visits his father's friend, Rehman, who is a doctor in a village. Soon, Anand falls in love with Soni, a simple village girl who is ostracised by society.

title: Gair Kaanooni
subTitle: Police Inspector Kapil Khanna realises that his baby boy has been switched with a girl child by the hospital and files a lawsuit against the owner, Robert Decosta while trying to find his missing son.

title: Deewaar: Let's Bring Our Heroes Home
subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

title: Trishul
subTitle: Born out of wedlock, Vijay grows up with deep resentment towards his biological father Raj, a wealthy industrialist who has been leading a comfortable life with his legitimate family in the big city.
